column5: Went out for a evening fish on sat nite with the wife and the youngest boy, was hoping for some walleye, but they were not cooperating, managed some nice pics of some tall ships and a nice storm cell that went over us.
You really captured the scary side of an approaching storm! Can't help but see those masts on the Tall Ship look like lightning rods.

You guys seemed to be going through rough waters by the looks of the background of the pics. Sorry that the eyes didn't cooperate more but thats the name of the game.  Great pics of the ships! Thanks for sharing Leechman
